articles.author: Stephen Swanson, WCCO Staff
articles.title: Video shows iconic home on Rapidan Dam partially collapsing into Blue Earth River in southern Minnesota - CBS Minnesota
articles.description: The raging Blue Earth River, which caused an abutment of the 114-year-old Rapidan Dam to partially fail, has now swallowed most of the iconic home that sits on a nearby embankment.
